<div id="pf33c8" class="pf w5b h238" data-page-no="33c8"><div class="pc pc33c8 w5b h238"><div class="t mbe1 xcb h49 y2aa1 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 6 </div><div class="t m295 x140 ha y2b61 ff2 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">May 9 </div><div class="t m2ec8 x2a ha5 y2bd ff1 fs1c fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SATAN&apos;S STRATAGEMS </div><div class="t m150 xb9 h71 y499 ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Whosoever he be of you that forsaketh not all that he hath, he cannot be My </div><div class="t ma13 xb7 h71 yd89 ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">disciple.&quot; Luke 14:33. </div><div class="t m1221 x15 h4 y5ff ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In every war resourceful men devise </div><div class="t m2b6 xb7 h4 y6f2 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">many sinister tricks to destroy the enemy. </div><div class="t ma50 xb7 h4 y320 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">They set up booby traps in the most un-</div><div class="t m3f5 xb7 h4 y1dd ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">expected places. When an unthinking soldier </div><div class="t ma7b xb7 h4 y6d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">touches some part of one of these, he sets </div><div class="t mf22 xb7 h4 y2eb ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">off an explosion that kills him and those </div><div class="t m6a4 xb7 h4 y618 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">near him. Retreating soldiers attach lethal </div><div class="t ma40 xb7 h4 y26 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">devices to items which are designed to </div><div class="t m1692 xb7 h4 y1a9 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">arouse the curiosity or cupidity of those </div><div class="t m13a xb7 h4 y221 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">who follow. Valuable binoculars, pistols, </div><div class="t m2ce xb7 h4 yf60 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">water bottles, and other articles are fixed </div><div class="t m9be xb7 h4 y380 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as alluring bait. As soon as a foolish soldier </div><div class="t m767 xb9 h4 y276 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">picks up one of these, he is blown to pieces. </div><div class="t maea xb9 h4 yc66 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">By his training and desire for self-preser-</div><div class="t m203 xb9 h4 y1ad ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">vation the soldier should have been on the </div><div class="t m618 xb9 h4 y169 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">alert for these booby traps. </div><div class="t m3d4 x15 h4 y32 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Satan employs ten thousand other strate-</div><div class="t m824 xb7 h4 y885 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">gems in most cunning deceptions. In the </div><div class="t m3a0 xb9 h4 y2037 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">parables that we shall study this week our </div><div class="t m3bc xb9 h4 ya3c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lord calls attention to some of the knavery </div><div class="t m7c1 xb9 h4 ye20 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">against which we should be continually on </div><div class="t m299 xb9 h4 ye24 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the alert. </div><div class="t m35a x95 h71 y589 ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON OUTLINE </div><div class="t m1b8 x8 h71 y6b0 ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m1f3 x46 h71 y6b0 ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Fields of Paradise </div><div class="t mda5 xb3 h71 ya70 ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Matt. 13:24 </div><div class="t maf6 x8 h71 y36a ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m195 x46 h71 y5bb ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">While Men Slept </div><div class="t m3cb xb3 h71 ybf7 ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Matt. 13:25 </div><div class="t m2d5 x8 h71 y8fb ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m23f x46 h71 y3c2 ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Counterfeit Grain </div><div class="t m2d0 xb3 h71 y275 ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mal. 3:18 </div><div class="t m443 x8 h71 y86b ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m114 x46 h71 y6f6 ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Devils Love a Vacuum </div><div class="t m7c7 x46 h71 y38 ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Matt. 12:43-45 </div><div class="t m5e1 x8 h71 yc33 ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t me80 x46 h71 y533 ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Gauging the Enemy </div><div class="t m54a x46 h71 y65b ff3 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Luke 14:31-33 </div><div c